4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals aiming to become proficient in cybersecurity without any prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, catering to a maximum of 16 participants. Students will develop a foundational understanding of Windows, Linux, networking, and server administration while acquiring practical skills in areas like cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Graduates receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. The course is available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop